<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Paper Submission Acknowledgement - Universal Journal of Green SciTech & Management</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      background-color: #f8f9fa; 
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 20px; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 700px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      background: white; 
      padding: 30px; 
      border-radius: 10px; 
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header { 
      text-align: center; 
      border-bottom: 3px solid #008080; 
      padding-bottom: 20px; 
      margin-bottom: 30px; 
    }
    .journal-title { 
      color: #008080; 
      font-size: 24px; 
      font-weight: bold; 
      margin: 0; 
    }
    .subtitle { 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 16px; 
      margin: 5px 0 0 0; 
    }
    h1 { 
      color: #2c3e50; 
      font-size: 20px; 
      margin-bottom: 20px; 
    }
    .info-box { 
      background-color: #f0f8f8; 
      border-left: 4px solid #008080; 
      padding: 20px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
    }
    .info-item { 
      margin: 8px 0; 
    }
    .label { 
      font-weight: bold; 
      color: #2c3e50; 
    }
    .track-button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      background-color: #008080; 
      color: white; 
      padding: 12px 25px; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      font-weight: bold; 
    }
    .track-button:hover { 
      background-color: #006666; 
    }
    .process-section { 
      background-color: #fff8f0; 
      border: 1px solid #ffd700; 
      padding: 20px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
    }
    .criteria-list { 
      padding-left: 20px; 
    }
    .criteria-list li { 
      margin: 5px 0; 
    }
    .contact-section { 
      background-color: #f5f5f5; 
      padding: 20px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 12px; 
      margin-top: 30px; 
      padding-top: 20px; 
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd; 
    }
    a { 
      color: #008080; 
      text-decoration: none; 
    }
    a:hover { 
      text-decoration: underline; 
    }
    .note { 
      background-color: #e8f4f8; 
      border: 1px solid #b3d9e6; 
      padding: 15px; 
      margin: 20px 0; 
      border-radius: 5px; 
      font-weight: bold; 
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2 class="journal-title">Universal Journal of Green Sci-Tech & Management</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Paper Submission Acknowledgement</p>
    </div>

    <h1>Dear {{name}},</h1>
    
    <p>Congratulations! We are pleased to inform you that your paper has been successfully submitted to the Universal Journal of Green Sci-Tech & Management (UJGSM).</p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">Registration ID:</span> {{trackingId}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">Paper Title:</span> {{manuscriptTitle}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">Corresponding Author:</span> {{name}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">Email:</span> {{email}}
      </div>
      <div class="info-item">
        <span class="label">Submission Date:</span> {{submissionDate}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>You can track your paper status using your registration ID and email address through our author portal.</p>
    <a href="{{trackUrl}}" class="track-button">Track Your Paper Status</a>

    <div class="note">
      Note: You will receive an acceptance or revision notification within 5-7 business days.
    </div>

    <div class="process-section">
      <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 0;">Peer Review Process</h3>
      <p>Your submission will undergo our double-blind peer review process. This typically takes 2-3 weeks to complete, depending on the number of review rounds required. All manuscripts are evaluated based on:</p>
      <ul class="criteria-list">
        <li>Originality and significance of the research</li>
        <li>Methodological rigor</li>
        <li>Clarity of presentation</li>
        <li>Alignment with journal's scope</li>
        <li>Ethical compliance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-section">
      <h3 style="color: #2c3e50; margin-top: 0;">Contact Information</h3>
      <p><strong>Journal Website:</strong> <a href="https://ujgsm.uorapublications.com">https://ujgsm.uorapublications.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Editorial Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:editor@uorapublications.com">editor@uorapublications.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Phone Support:</strong> +91 9766930707 (Available Mon-Fri, 10AM-5PM IST)</p>
      
      <h4 style="color: #2c3e50;">Support Options:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Email your questions to <a href="mailto:editor@uorapublications.com">editor@uorapublications.com</a> (response within 2 business days)</li>
        <li>For manuscript-related inquiries, please include your registration ID in all communications</li>
        <li>Schedule a consultation call through our online booking system</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Best regards,<br><strong>UJGSM Editorial Team</strong></p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p><strong>Universal Journal of Green SciTech & Management (UJGSM)</strong></p>
      <p>Published by Universal Oneness Research Association (UORA)</p>
      <p>Registered Address: E-1/8 Mathura Nagar, N-6, Cidco, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, Maharashtra 431003, India</p>
      <p>ISSN: XXXX-XXXX | Frequency: Bi-monthly | Open Access: CC BY 4.0</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 11px;">
        <strong>Confidentiality Notice:</strong> This email contains confidential information intended solely for the addressed recipient. 
        If you are not the intended recipient, please notify us immediately and delete it from your system.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
        Please consider the environment before printing this email.<br>
        This is a system generated email. Please include your registration ID ({{trackingId}}) in all correspondence.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>